                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; font-family: GT-Sectra-Book, GT-Sectra, serif; font-variant-numeric: lining-nums; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.56; letter-spacing: 0.1px; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">We may partner with ad networks and other ad serving providers (&ldquo;Advertising Providers&rdquo;) that serve ads on behalf of us and others on non-affiliated platforms. Some of those ads may be personalized, meaning that they are intended to be relevant to you based on information Advertising Providers collect about your use of the Service and other sites or apps over time, including information about relationships among different browsers and devices. This type of advertising is known as interest-based advertising.</span></p>
