                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; font-family: GT-Sectra-Book, GT-Sectra, serif; font-variant-numeric: lining-nums; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.56; letter-spacing: 0.1px; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DAA.appchoices" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: black; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">DAA AppChoices Android</span></a></p>
