                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; font-family: GT-Sectra-Book, GT-Sectra, serif; font-variant-numeric: lining-nums; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.56; letter-spacing: 0.1px; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">Note that choosing to opt out will not stop advertising from appearing in your browser. It may make the ads you see less relevant to your interests. Advertising Providers may continue to collect data for other purposes, including analytics and other operational purposes.</span></p>
                        <p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; font-family: GT-Sectra-Book, GT-Sectra, serif; font-variant-numeric: lining-nums; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.56; letter-spacing: 0.1px; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">If you delete your cookies, reset your device advertising identifier, or use a different browser or mobile device, you will need to renew your opt-out choice. You may also be able to limit data collection for advertising purposes using tools available on your device. Additionally, your browser may offer tools to limit the use of cookies or to delete cookies; however, if you use these tools, the Service may not function as intended. We may also work with third parties that collect data about your use of the Service and other sites or apps over time for non-advertising purposes. We use Google Analytics and other third-party services to improve the performance of the Service and for analytics and marketing purposes. For more information about how Google Analytics collects and uses data when you use the Service, visit&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: black; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/</span></a><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">, and to opt out of Google Analytics, visit&nbsp;</span><a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: black; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/</span></a><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">.</span></p>
