               <li class="cd-faq__item">
                  <a class="cd-faq__trigger" href="#0"><span>WILL MY ORDER BE DELAYED?</span></a>
                  <div class="cd-faq__content">
                     <div class="text-component">
                        <p>While most orders are shipping on-time, due to carrier delays or COVID-19 and government restrictions in your area, your order may experience some shipping and fulfillment delays. We are actively routing orders to the optimal facility for processing to ensure we can get your order to you as quickly as possible.</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- cd-faq__content -->
               </li>
               <li class="cd-faq__item">
                  <a class="cd-faq__trigger" href="#0"><span>COULD MY PACKAGE BE SENT TO/FROM A DIFFERENT FACILITY OR BY A DIFFERENT CARRIER THAN I’M USED TO SEEING?</span></a>
