                     <div class="text-component">
                        <p>Yes. To get orders to customers as quickly as possible, we may be making adjustments to our general business operations.</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- cd-faq__content -->
               </li>
               <li class="cd-faq__item">
