                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- cd-faq__content -->
               </li>
               <li class="cd-faq__item">
                  <a class="cd-faq__trigger" href="#0"><span>WILL MY SALES ORDERS AND RELATED PAYOUTS BE DELAYED?</span></a>
                  <div class="cd-faq__content">
