                        <p>While most sales orders are shipping on-time, due to carrier delays or COVID-19 and government restrictions in your area, your sales order may experience shipping delays. This may affect the time it takes for your item to arrive at one of our facilities, and thus affect when you will be paid out for your item.</p>
